      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start. for my paper though, I need to get deeper into the actual outcomes. when looking at the empirical data from similar past reforms, which of those two perspectives—the growth/job creation argument or the widening wealth gap argument—has a more statistically significant track record? like, which one do the actual numbers tend to support more clearly?",
